Class ReviewDTO

java.lang.Object
it.uninsubria.dto.ReviewDTO
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ReviewDTO extends Object implements Serializable
Data Transfer Object for Review information. This class is responsible for encapsulating review data to transfer between client and server. Uses public fields for direct access without getters and setters.

  • Constructor Details

    • ReviewDTO

      public ReviewDTO(String usr_id, String rest_id, String customer_msg, Integer rating, String rest_rep)
      Complete constructor with all review information. The restaurant reply field can be null if no reply has been made.
      Parameters:
      usr_id - ID of the user who created the review
      rest_id - ID of the restaurant being reviewed
      customer_msg - Review message from the customer
      rating - Star rating (1-5)
      rest_rep - Optional reply from restaurant owner (can be null)

    • ReviewDTO

      public ReviewDTO(String usr_id, String rest_id, String customer_msg, Integer rating)
      Constructor for a new review without a restaurant reply.
      Parameters:
      usr_id - ID of the user who created the review
      rest_id - ID of the restaurant being reviewed
      customer_msg - Review message from the customer
      rating - Star rating (1-5)
